BT /F1 11 Tf 72 373 Td (or what confidentiality obligations apply. The project goal is to reduce manual search) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 358 Td (effort by building a reproducible NLP pipeline that finds relevant clauses and extracts) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 343 Td (concise answers.) Tj ET
