BT /F1 11 Tf 72 686 Td (The baseline performs strongly on the prepared dataset because the questions are tightly) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 671 Td (grounded in specific legal clauses and the expected evidence spans are present in the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 656 Td (indexed text. This validates the retrieval and evidence-grounding workflow, while still) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 641 Td (leaving room for deeper transformer evaluation on larger public legal QA datasets.) Tj ET
